Klemm et&#x000a0;al. (<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR18">2012</xref>) introduced the following version of a prepartition encoding. Here, an arbitrary function <inline-formula id="IEq292"><alternatives><tex-math id="M595">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
