</p></sec><sec id="Sec22"><title>Maximum Clique Problems</title><p id="Par99">Figure&#x000a0;<xref rid="Fig4" ref-type="fig">4</xref> shows the time evolution of the cost of adaptive walks on the encoded landscapes of graph cliques encoded by node sequences. The figure caption contains details on the instances and relevant definitions can be found in Sect.&#x000a0;<xref rid="Sec13" ref-type="sec">3.4.6</xref>. We plot the difference with the minimum cost <inline-formula id="IEq606"><alternatives><tex-math id="M1245">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
